track_notes: Except the landscape, there is no interest to activate on this summit. There is a lot of radio activity (TV-GSM-Relay) that makes QRM even on VHF. If you have a 4 Wheeel drive you can even reach the summit by car!!!
track_title: Easy and short path to summit

track_notes: Park the car at the Col de Brouis, the walk is easy on a forest road until the summit, or you can use the foot path nice also. You will find pylones, and you can carry on a little bit down to la croix de Roudoule in FFF-0103
Easy one, can be done via large track or small single (as show here). Kids friendly. QRM at the top.
